            Ready to find out what your data <span style="font-family:'Lora',serif;font-style:italic;font-weight:500;color:#455A7C;">can — and cannot —</span> prove to funders?
          </h2>
          <p style="margin-top:22px;font-family:'Roboto',sans-serif;font-size:17px;color:#4d525e;line-height:1.6;">We are selecting 5 nonprofit design partners for a no-cost Impact Reporting &amp; Data Readiness Assessment. If your organization is creating impact but struggling to prove it clearly, start with a Reporting Readiness Call.</p>
